{
  "stem": "5761.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then I was sent to an officers' school in Netanya.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I became an officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was assigned to Hativat Givati, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which was one of the brigade which was known of the best brigades in Israel, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which we lost about 350 soldiers during the war.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was in Givati till I was wounded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And first time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and this was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the big battle when the Arab nation's neighbors decided to attack Israel.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And our brigade was in Negev, which was the, the hottest battlefields in Israel at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was an assistant commander [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] near a bridge which was connecting Egyptian side with Israeli side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they decided to attack our positions, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which we were there, about 180 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were advancing with tanks, full battlefield dress, and you know, planes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We digged in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we fought them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We lost a lot of people, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] including our commander got wounded very hard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we connected with the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he connected with the headquarters and, and described the battle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, and he asked who takes over the command.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And headquarters assigned me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I took over the command.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we succeeded to push back the Egyptian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Then they got it through the radio that I got wounded, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which I, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I got wounded, and I got killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but it wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But we fought.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We managed to push them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we got reinforcement.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
